{"tid":1721240,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【停？】同大家重溫一下優品360職員點樣配合黑警捉人","createTime":"2019-11-14T15:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T08:08:48.000Z","uid":85390,"like":102,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"8f9e8d18ea1fed65f375e20f46dc443b61d44d58","tid":1721240,"uid":85390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:12:41.000Z","msg":"可能呢件事比較少人關注，所以無乜人記得。<br />\n<br />\n10月13號係新都會廣場，蒙面便衣狗係黑品360捉左3男四女手足呀！睇下面條片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=ocyBzxL0znQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DocyBzxL0znQ&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6z632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=f193ba99\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=ocyBzxL0znQ</a><br />\n<br />\n而啲職員當時做緊乜？ <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪就係配合啲狗落閘，困住哂手足，連街坊都入唔到去救人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdUvuYQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkdUvuYQ.png&h=c0de47cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gs47xcm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgs47xcm.png&h=1bed17e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YRx805R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYRx805R.png&h=6311a46c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7CwNxcG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7CwNxcG.png&h=91bb46bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>你地班友依家同我講原諒佢地？ 守承諾？<br />\n咁係咪當被捕同受傷手足係condom? 咁福建幫嘅仇又點計？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我屌哂你地老母，成撚日掛住搶佔道德高地，你地班友真係打算用愛與和平搞革命就死得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9146e6c8dd978a86d8a6a9243036ea862d5999de","tid":1721240,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:14:11.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6855300695c550713e85e554055ac25a6e5e88f2","tid":1721240,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2eae554180703be0ffde6f72b2c7e2242327c6f","tid":1721240,"uid":212182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:15:18.000Z","msg":"不會原諒"},{"pid":"3549071e2d576184ca580b34238e70ea3313d69e","tid":1721240,"uid":203619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:16:29.000Z","msg":"屌哂你地老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d115e7ebca4227127eceabd6e1a4e1e40bc8eb1c","tid":1721240,"uid":77473,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:16:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕不原諒福建360<br />\n斬左幾多手足 <br />\n幾多人爆肺斷手<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"a170a6020ddd05dfc8d74d68f2d4347bfb1ffe5a","tid":1721240,"uid":16029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:17:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f69c4d3bec1ca6c3b84c0e18c1999bc0bf520f10","tid":1721240,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:17:22.000Z","msg":"曱甴平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9fb82271f036e464d9f5720259781735189